            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "財經｜國泰8月上調燃油附加費  長途航班加幅逾四成",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\" data-component=\"blocks\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"財經｜國泰8月上調燃油附加費  長途航班加幅逾四成\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"502\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/lo/mysterio/api/49b0d0ce980e8683d284f9ba2e12c935cf1463332015d8c1421a6fba516afa28/lightyear_networkapi/resizefill_w960;quality_80;format_webp/https:%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Ffortune_insight_694%2Fdbddec0f78d2a1ab4bc25a6950c04ffb\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">財經｜國泰8月上調燃油附加費  長途航班加幅逾四成</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">受中東局勢升溫帶動國際油價回升影響，國泰航空宣布由8月起調高<a data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":0,\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\"}' data-ylk=\"elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;\" href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/tag/燃油附加費\" rel=\"\">燃油附加費</a>，這亦是自4月以來首次加價。長途航班加幅最顯著，相關費用升至1,362元，較原來增加約41%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">按新安排，香港往內地航班的燃油附加費由165元調高至198元，升幅約20%；往來香港與西南太平洋、北美、歐洲、中東及非洲的長途航班，由965元升至1,362元；往來南亞次大陸的航班則由448元加至633元；其他航線則由241元上調至339元。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-43a58b36-7ad6-380a-900d-950aacfe54f5-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">國泰表示，航空燃油價格在4月曾見高位，其後一度回落，但近期因中東局勢再趨緊張而重新上升。今次調整後的附加費水平仍低於4月高峰，5月起亦曾多次下調價格，而現行機制可較靈活反映油價變化。國泰又指，將繼續每兩周檢視燃油附加費水平。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT Telegram: <br/><a data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":\"0\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yLinkText\":\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2M63TRO;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2M63TRO\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2M63TRO</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Subscribe FORTUNE INSIGHT YouTube channel:<br/><a data-yga='{\"yInteractivityType\":\"0\",\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yLinkText\":\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\"}' data-ylk=\"slk:http://bit.ly/2FgJTen;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas;\" href=\"http://bit.ly/2FgJTen\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2FgJTen</a></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93-%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B08%E6%9C%88%E4%B8%8A%E8%AA%BF%E7%87%83%E6%B2%B9%E9%99%84%E5%8A%A0%E8%B2%BB-%E9%95%B7%E9%80%94%E8%88%AA%E7%8F%AD%E5%8A%A0%E5%B9%85%E9%80%BE%E5%9B%9B%E6%88%90-081713373.html",
